Invocation Name: retro album rock
des: Take a trip into Progressive Radio's past -- one year at a time! Each week, we spotlight a different "Feature Year" of deep album cuts, classic rock favorites, one-hit wonders, rare tracks and crossover songs from other musical genres. Plus, memories of TV, movie, news, sports and other lifestyle events from that particular year!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
